history.content:
Data Science Society is recruiting for data curious students for Spring 2020!

 

https://www.facebook.com/events/627816348049231/

 

Come chat with us at our recruitment events:

  • Case Workshop: Jan 29th 8-9pm in Barrows 20
  • Meet the Society: Jan 30th 7-9pm at FSM Patio

 

Applications
----------------------------
Committee App: https://tinyurl.com/DSS-SP20-CMApp
General Member App: https://tinyurl.com/DSS-SP20-GMApp
DeCal Student App: bit.ly/decal2020

 

DSS is UC Berkeley’s first undergraduate student organization centered on Data Science (est. 2016) and its interdisciplinary applications.

Together we focus on developing educational workshops in collaborative environments, hosting professional events to grow your network, and conducting consulting projects with top tech companies to help you gain experience. Our goal is to build an inclusive and accessible community where students of all levels and backgrounds can dive into the world of data science.
